# Pre-rendered tool pages are real files on disk (dist/tools/<slug>/index.html).
# Cloudflare Pages serves matching static assets BEFORE applying these rules,
# so those URLs resolve to their own HTML with correct titles/meta.
# Everything else (unknown paths, /, /tools) falls back to the SPA shell.
/          /tools/image-compressor    302
/tools     /tools/image-compressor    302
/*         /index.html                200
